gr.interamerican.bo2.impl.open.utils
Class Exceptions

java.lang.Object
  gr.interamerican.bo2.impl.open.utils.Exceptions

public class Exceptions
extends Object

Utility class that provides methods that create exceptions. Some exceptions are thrown almost the same way in various different cases across the project. This class provides utility methods that throw these exceptions.
